{"tid":811471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"超蓮愛慕者搵上門","createTime":"2018-09-08T23:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T07:53:47.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"30ac0810925c1ca1f6c5ea523fbdcd5ef3060cae","tid":811471,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T23:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180907/large/07ec4p13newe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F07ec4p13newe.jpg&h=6b3fb8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賭王三房索千金何超蓮喺銅鑼灣開咗麵舖，成日都有粉絲去捧場，原來近日仲有「愛慕者」搵上門，去到佢住嘅布力徑大宅等佢。超蓮承認為咗呢件事報警：「佢喺度好多日啦，成日都等我，我哋啲保安都好熟佢，都唔會畀佢入嚟我屋企，嗰日我阿媽出車，佢入咗嚟，佢哋覺得要報警，所以就報咗警，其實佢喺度好多次，都費事拉佢，但係佢行埋入嚟先報警。」超蓮提到該男子曾送禮品上門：「信、花、公仔，好似送過部琴仔。」"},{"pid":"01475c08c3a84877a377491a6753a74207107b9f","tid":811471,"uid":44673,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T23:43:30.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打？"},{"pid":"7b29a57a45ac1e6b23a90c64757d3ca77289c83c","tid":811471,"uid":172950,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T23:46:42.000Z","msg":"佢講漏左,其實我仲送過我地嘅合照比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9896e2653324d74c65c01ce8082a9a27cf5ae6","tid":811471,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T00:15:10.000Z","msg":"啲食客都係保鑣"},{"pid":"4357031fbe9d3f9113ad764291f155cae0c3e832","tid":811471,"uid":69937,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T00:17:09.000Z","msg":"睇左做 超愛慕蓮者搵上門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef2c242985aab3fce77f6befffca2c108cbf9d6","tid":811471,"uid":139244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯余慕蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8ffbcb5b291271253bb6b0ad197b9e55b4ac07","tid":811471,"uid":130626,"like"